name: Jakarta Bowling Center
description:
From the day I went to a bowling alley for the first time.
Not sure how old the place was, but everything seemed and smelled like from decades ago including this automatic scorer monitor that also played trippy retro animations between turns. I sucked the game and didn't even manage to take other picture but this photo really helps me remember every funny little details about that day.

Captured and edited with my 2015 ASUS Zenfone 4 - A400CG Android phone.
